{"tid":2093770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳弘毅：國安法是中央提出的新社會契約","createTime":"2020-07-04T05:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T00:25:01.000Z","uid":48040,"like":49,"dislike":187,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"96cb4abcbfef60a8703dd9f3588b87ae23485b91","tid":2093770,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"陳弘毅你唔好玷污「社會契約」呢個詞。<br />\n社會契約需要得到全體社會成員同意。但事實上，香港人是在國安法頒布之後才睇到國安法的全文。<br />\n而且，「社會契約」永遠都係人民提出，政府遵守。陳弘毅居然顛倒因果，話統治者提出「社會契約」，人民要遵守。咁簡單的邏輯都唔清楚，我很懷疑他點解可以擔任教授。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535741-20200704.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535741-20200704.htm&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=7236cabb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535741-20200704.htm&h=ecff76c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535741-20200704.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\nTwitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1279288206790324225?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1279288206790324225%3Fs%3D20&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=53a3ea0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1279288206790324225%3Fs%3D20&h=05246c4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1279288206790324225?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"7f2a06790b7230e8aca2b2089b36a9fbbc02a594","tid":2093770,"uid":3457,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"依加就係講緊條野唔清唔楚呀"},{"pid":"8a82eeb94188c39007a5b24597ac567fd74aaf20","tid":2093770,"uid":250948,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"係咪收左乜野利益咁講"},{"pid":"e00e9859789a1416d2088686bfe457